begin_memory_text: My partner an I talked about our locations and where we were from as well as how the COVID19 pandemic has affected our areas and the people we know.  We also talked about Prolific and this Better Labs Study a bit.

critical_positive: I think what worked well with the conversation was that we both had the same core beliefs in terms of science and health.  We both had the same views on politics and of wanting to help others.  She was a good listener and I know I talked more but I hope I was as well.
